### Telegram Downloader API Test
### File ini bisa digunakan dengan REST Client extension di VS Code
### Atau bisa copy-paste ke Postman/Insomnia

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### 2. Info API
GET http://localhost:3000/

### 3. Download Media dari Channel Publik
POST http://localhost:3000/api/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "link": "https://t.me/channelName/123"
}

### 4. Download Media dari Channel Privat
POST http://localhost:3000/api/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "link": "https://t.me/c/channelId/messageId"
}

### 5. Test Error - Link tidak valid
POST http://localhost:3000/api/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "link": "https://invalid-link.com"
}

### 6. Test Error - Link kosong
POST http://localhost:3000/api/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "link": ""
}

